D.q[988] = "I see you\'ve found some GM Wabbit blood. Well, I need to have it analysed. Go ask Otomai, the alchemist, he should be able to do it for you.";
D.q[7816] = "Thanks for your help.\nWhile you were gone, I tried to convince Grimmben to go with you, but he refused. That lousy pighead was worried I\'d get hurt by the forest creatures if I were on my own, and so he thought he\'d sort it out better himself.";
D.q[7818] = "Nice of you to come back, but you could\'ve avoided bringing so many Sabredons with you... I\'ll take a dozen, you take care of the remaining three.";
D.q[7601] = "You might not believe me but I have, hehe, freed the soul of this monster in my bedroom... If you really want to go in there, don\'t mind the mess. I regularly hunt the cockroaches that infest that room and I don\'t have the time to clear stuff away. \nOne last tip: be careful because my room is quite small, and the Manitou Zoth tends to summon spirits to help. You might be overwhelmed quicker than you think. \nDo you still feel up to challenging the Manitou Zoth?";
D.q[7615] = "Haven\'t you heard? The two terrible dragons, Grozilla and Grasmera, have been defeated.\nYou probably don\'t know what I\'m talking about, so let me tell you a little more about them.";
D.q[7826] = "Hello, welcome to our would-be Ice Village. It doesn\'t look much at the moment but you\'ll see, in a few years it will be the number one tourist attraction.";
